{"markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"","page-layout":"full","toc":false},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n```{=html}\n<section style=\"padding: 4rem 0 2rem;\">\n  <div class=\"section-label\">Who I am</div>\n  <h1>About Me</h1>\n  <hr class=\"neon-rule\">\n</section>\n```\n\n```{=html}\n<div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; padding-bottom: 4rem;\">\n  <div>\n    <img\n      src=\"images/profile.jpg\"\n      alt=\"Raunit Budhiraja\"\n      style=\"width:100%; border-radius:16px; border:1px solid #252535; filter: grayscale(20%);\"\n    />\n    <div style=\"margin-top: 1.5rem; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.6rem;\">\n      <a href=\"mailto:raunit.budhiraja@mail.dcu.ie\" class=\"btn-ghost\" style=\"justify-content:center;\">\n        ✉ raunit.budhiraja@mail.dcu.ie\n      </a>\n      <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/raunitbudhiraja/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn-ghost\" style=\"justify-content:center;\">\n        LinkedIn →\n      </a>\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/raunitbudhiraja\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn-ghost\" style=\"justify-content:center;\">\n        GitHub →\n      </a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div>\n    <p style=\"font-size:1.1rem; color:#e2e2e2; line-height:1.9;\">\n      Hi, I'm Raunit — a Business Analytics student at Dublin City University with a genuine interest\n      in the space where data meets decision-making. I grew up comfortable with numbers but\n      fell in love with code once I realised how much you could do with a 40-line Python script\n      and a decent dataset.\n    </p>\n\n    <p style=\"margin-top:1.2rem;\">\n      My academic work sits across data analysis, machine learning, and business strategy.\n      Outside of lectures, I spend time building small projects — usually starting from a question\n      I genuinely want to answer, then figuring out the tools from there.\n    </p>\n\n    <p>\n      I'm particularly drawn to projects where the output is something a non-technical stakeholder\n      can actually use — a clean dashboard, a single-number forecast, or a well-told data story.\n      That intersection of rigour and communication is where I want to keep getting better.\n    </p>\n\n    <div style=\"margin-top: 2.5rem;\">\n      <div class=\"section-label\">Education</div>\n      <div class=\"timeline\" style=\"margin-top:1.2rem;\">\n        <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n          <div class=\"tl-date\">2022 – Present</div>\n          <h3>BSc Business Analytics</h3>\n          <p>Dublin City University (DCU)</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n          <div class=\"tl-date\">2022</div>\n          <h3>Leaving Certificate</h3>\n          <p>Secondary School, India</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n---\n\n```{=html}\n<section style=\"padding: 3rem 0 5rem;\">\n  <div class=\"section-label\">Compliance Training</div>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom:1.5rem;\">Kubicle Certifications</h2>\n  <p>As part of the BAA1104 module, I completed the following Kubicle courses covering data governance and ethics:</p>\n\n  <div class=\"card-grid\" style=\"margin-top:1.5rem;\">\n    <div class=\"project-card\" style=\"cursor:default;\">\n      <div class=\"card-tag\">✓ Completed</div>\n      <h3>Introduction to GDPR</h3>\n      <p>Principles of data protection, lawful processing, and individual rights under EU law.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"project-card\" style=\"cursor:default;\">\n      <div class=\"card-tag\">✓ Completed</div>\n      <h3>Data Security: Keeping Your Information Safe</h3>\n      <p>Introduction to information security concepts, threats, and mitigation strategies.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"project-card\" style=\"cursor:default;\">\n      <div class=\"card-tag\">✓ Completed</div>\n      <h3>Data Security: Handling Data Securely</h3>\n      <p>Security protocols, responsible handling of sensitive data, and organisational practices.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"project-card\" style=\"cursor:default;\">\n      <div class=\"card-tag\">✓ Completed</div>\n      <h3>Data Ethics & Risk: Introduction</h3>\n      <p>Ethical dimensions of data collection, bias, fairness, and algorithmic accountability.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"project-card\" style=\"cursor:default;\">\n      <div class=\"card-tag\">✓ Completed</div>\n      <h3>Data Ethics & Risk: Applying Ethical Thinking</h3>\n      <p>Practical frameworks for responsible data use in real business and research contexts.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n```\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n```{=html}\n<section style=\"padding: 4rem 0 2rem;\">\n  <div class=\"section-label\">Who I am</div>\n  <h1>About Me</h1>\n  <hr class=\"neon-rule\">\n</section>\n```\n\n```{=html}\n<div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; padding-bottom: 4rem;\">\n  <div>\n    <img\n      src=\"images/profile.jpg\"\n      alt=\"Raunit Budhiraja\"\n      style=\"width:100%; border-radius:16px; border:1px solid #252535; filter: grayscale(20%);\"\n    />\n    <div style=\"margin-top: 1.5rem; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.6rem;\">\n      <a href=\"mailto:raunit.budhiraja@mail.dcu.ie\" class=\"btn-ghost\" style=\"justify-content:center;\">\n        ✉ raunit.budhiraja@mail.dcu.ie\n      </a>\n      <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/raunitbudhiraja/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn-ghost\" style=\"justify-content:center;\">\n        LinkedIn →\n      </a>\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/raunitbudhiraja\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn-ghost\" style=\"justify-content:center;\">\n        GitHub →\n      </a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div>\n    <p style=\"font-size:1.1rem; color:#e2e2e2; line-height:1.9;\">\n      Hi, I'm Raunit — a Business Analytics student at Dublin City University with a genuine interest\n      in the space where data meets decision-making. I grew up comfortable with numbers but\n      fell in 